{{Infobox UK legislation |short_title=The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009<ref>The citation of this Act by this [[short title]] is authorised by [http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2009/22/section/270 section 270(1)] of this Act.</ref> |parliament=Parliament of the United Kingdom |long_title=An Act to make provision about apprenticeships, education, training and children's services; to amend the [[Employment Rights Act 1996]]; to establish the [[Young People's Learning Agency for England]], the office of [[Chief Executive of Skills Funding]], the [[Office of Qualifications and Examinations Regulation]] and the [[School Support Staff Negotiating Body]] and to make provision about those bodies and that office; to make provision about the [[Qualifications and Curriculum Authority]]; to make provision about schools and institutions within the further education sector; to make provision about student loans; and for connected purposes. |year=2009 |statute_book_chapter=2009 c 22 |introduced_by= |territorial_extent= |royal_assent=12 November 2009 |commencement= |repeal_date= |amendments= |related_legislation= |repealing_legislation= |status= |original_text=http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2009/22/contents/enacted |legislation_history=http://services.parliament.uk/bills/2008-09/apprenticeshipsskillschildrenandlearning.html |revised_text=http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2009/22/contents |}}
'''The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009''' (c 22) is an [[Act of Parliament|Act]] of the [[Parliament of the United Kingdom]]. It alters the law relating to education.
The precursors of this Act were the [[white paper]] "Raising Expectations: Enabling the system to deliver" published in March 2008 and a "Draft Apprenticeships Bill" published in July of that year.<ref>Explanatory notes, [http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2009/22/notes/division/2 paragraphs 4 and 5]</ref>
==Commencement== See [http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2009/22/section/269 section 269] of the Act and the following Orders made thereunder: *[http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2009/3317/contents/made The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009 (Commencement No. 1 and Saving Provision) Order 2009] (S.I. 2009/3317 (C. 148)) *[http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2010/303/contents/made The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009 (Commencement No. 2 and Transitional and Saving Provisions) Order 2010] (S.I. 2010/303 (C. 25)) *[http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2010/1891/contents/made The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009 (Commencement No. 2 (Amendment) and Transitional Provision) Order 2010] (S.I. 2010/1891 (C. 99)) *[http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2011/882/contents/made The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009 (Commencement No. 2 and Transitional and Saving Provisions) Order 2010 (Amendment) Order 2011] (S.I. 2011/882 (C. 35)) *[http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2010/1151/contents/made The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009 (Commencement No. 3 and Transitional and Transitory Provisions) and (Commencement No. 2 (Amendment)) Order 2010] (S.I. 2010/1151 (C. 75)) *[http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2010/1702/contents/made The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009 (Commencement No. 3 (Amendment)) Order 2010] (S.I. 2010/1702 (C. 88)) *[http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2010/2374/contents/made The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009 (Commencement No. 4) Order 2010] (S.I. 2010/2374 (C. 115)) *[http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2011/200/contents/made The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009 (Commencement No. 5) Order 2011] (S.I. 2011/200 (C. 10)) *[http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2009/3341/contents/made The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009 (Commencement No. 1) (Wales) Order 2009] (S.I. 2009/3341 (W. 292) (C. 152)) *[http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2010/2413/contents/made The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009 (Commencement No. 2 and Transitional Provisions) (Wales) Order 2010] (S.I. 2010/2413 (W. 207) (C. 118)) *[http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2011/829/contents/made The Apprenticeships, Skills, Children and Learning Act 2009 (Commencement No. 3) (Wales) Order 2011] (S.I. 2011/829 (W. 124) (C. 33))
